sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Application<br/>(localhost) HTTP

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: Authenticated Request Proxying

    Client->>Proxy: HTTPS Request (ANY path)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Client Cert / OIDC JWT
    activate Proxy

    Note over Proxy: Path Filter: check --ignore-paths

    alt Bearer Token Auth
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: TokenReview Response<br/>(authenticated user identity)
    else OIDC JWT Auth
        Note over Proxy: Verify JWT signature against cached JWKS<br/>Extract username/groups from claims
    else x509 Client Cert
        Note over Proxy: Verify client cert against --client-ca-file<br/>Extract CN as username, O as groups
    end

    Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authorization.k8s.io/v1/subjectaccessreviews<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview Response<br/>(allowed: true/false)

    alt Authorized
        Note over Proxy: Inject auth headers:<br/>X-Forwarded-User, X-Forwarded-Groups
        Proxy->>Upstream: Forward Request<br/>HTTP (localhost)
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    else Denied
        Proxy-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end
    deactivate Proxy

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(openshift-monitoring)

    Prom->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (prometheus-k8s SA)
    activate Proxy

    Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST tokenreviews<br/>(authenticate prometheus-k8s SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: TokenReview: authenticated as<br/>system:serviceaccount:openshift-monitoring:prometheus-k8s

    Note over Proxy: Hardcoded Authorizer:<br/>Allow prometheus-k8s SA on GET /metrics<br/>(skips SubjectAccessReview)

    Proxy->>Upstream: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (localhost)
    Upstream-->>Proxy: Metrics Response<br/>(Prometheus format)
    Proxy-->>Prom: HTTPS Metrics Response
    deactivate Proxy
